I"¡<p>This week we had a special guest for our weekly seminar in our cryptocurrency group. <a href="https://scholar.google.dk/citations?user=s6Km5yQAAAAJ&amp;hl=en">Dominik Harz</a> visited us to present his work on how to design collateral in blockchain systems. In particular, the explained his framework <a href="">Balance: Dynamic Adjustment of Cryptocurrency Deposits</a>, he also presented a very didactical explanation of the recent fresh loan attacks.</p>

